# Run tests after every change

After making any code change, always run the test suite inside Docker before declaring the task complete:

```bash
make docker-test
```

- If it exits 0 — the change is good, proceed.
- If it exits non-zero — fix the failures before finishing. Do not leave the task in a broken state.

This applies to every edit: source files, test files, config files, or the Dockerfile itself.
